	<p n="1">In the year Vṛṣa <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>vi<hi rend="grantha">ṣu</hi></foreign></supplied>, current <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>cellum</foreign></supplied> in the Vikrama era <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>varuṣattil</foreign></supplied>, month of Cittirai, <supplied reason="subaudible">day</supplied> 1 <gap reason="lost"/></p>

	<p n="1-2">The document <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>paṭṭayam</foreign></supplied> that ... gave ...</p>
	
	<p n="2-8">...</p>
	
	<p n="9">This is the signature of <gap reason="lost"/>kūttamutali.</p>
	
	<p n="9">Let them enjoy <supplied reason="subaudible">this</supplied> as long as the moon and the sun according to<note>Literally: "in".</note> this decision.</p>
	
	<p n="9-10"><gap reason="lost"/> this la<supplied reason="lost">nd</supplied> <gap reason="lost"/></p>
	
